official_title: Follow-up Study of Growth, Safety, and Efficacy of an Infant Formula for Healthy Term Infants
inclusion_criteria:
* Subjects who enrolled and completed the previous phase of the clinical trial: NCT04218929 "Evaluation of Growth, Safety, and Efficacy of an Infant Formula for Healthy Term Infants"
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 16 Weeks
Must have maximum age of 19 Weeks
exclusion_criteria: * Subjects who did not enroll in the previous phase of the clinical trial: NCT04218929 "Evaluation of Growth, Safety, and Efficacy of an Infant Formula for Healthy Term Infants"
